    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "sd = 10"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 17,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "[[<AxesSubplot:> <AxesSubplot:>]\n",
      " [<AxesSubplot:> <AxesSubplot:>]]\n",
      "0 0\n",
      "0 1\n",
      "1 0\n",
      "1 1\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 720x720 with 4 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "mean = (0, 0)\n",
    "cov1 = [[1, 0],\n",
    "       [0, 1]]\n",
    "cov2 = [[1, 0],\n",
    "       [0, 2]]\n",
    "cov3 = [[1, -1],\n",
    "       [-1, 1]]\n",
    "cov4 = [[1, -0.5],\n",
    "       [-0.5, 1]]\n",
    "covs = [cov1, cov2, cov3, cov4]\n",
    "cmaps = [\"Blues_r\", \"Reds_r\", \"Greens_r\", \"Purples_r\"]\n",
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,2,figsize=(10,10), sharex=True, sharey=True)\n",
    "print(axs)\n",
    "k=0\n",
    "np.random.seed(sd);\n",
    "for idx, cov in enumerate(covs):\n",
    "    data = np.random.multivariate_normal(mean, cov, 500)\n",
    "    # plt.scatter(data[:,0], data[:,1])\n",
    "    r = k//2\n",
    "    c = k%2\n",
    "    plt.sca(axs[r][c])\n",
    "    sns.kdeplot(x=data[:,0], y=data[:,1], bw_method=.99, cmap=cmaps[idx])#, shade=False, bw=.15)\n",
    "    if r > 0:\n",
    "        plt.xlabel(r'$x_1$', fontsize=20)\n",
    "    if c == 0: \n",
    "        plt.ylabel(r'$x_2$', fontsize=20, rotation='horizontal')\n",
    "    plt.title('ABCD'[k], fontsize=25)\n",
    "    plt.axhline(0, color='black')\n",
    "    plt.axvline(0, color='black')\n",
    "    plt.xlim([-max(np.abs(plt.axis())), max(np.abs(plt.axis()))])\n",
    "    plt.ylim([-max(np.abs(plt.axis())), max(np.abs(plt.axis()))])\n",
    "    plt.grid()\n",
    "    k+=1\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "fig.savefig('cov.pdf')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "np.random.seed(sd);\n",
    "# cmaps = [\"Blues_r\", \"Reds_r\", \"Greens_r\", \"Purples_r\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,2,figsize=(10,10), sharex=True, sharey=True)\n",
    "colors = ['b', 'r', 'g', 'purple']\n",
    "k = 0\n",
    "for idx, cov in enumerate(covs):\n",
    "    data = np.random.multivariate_normal(mean, cov, 100)\n",
    "    r = k//2\n",
    "    c = k%2\n",
    "    plt.sca(axs[r,c])\n",
    "#     sns.kdeplot(data[:,0], data[:,1], bw=.99, cmap=cmaps[idx])#, shade=False, bw=.15)\n",
    "    plt.scatter(data[:,0], data[:,1], color=colors[k])\n",
    "    if r > 0:\n",
    "        plt.xlabel(r'$x_1$', fontsize=20)\n",
    "    if c == 0: \n",
    "        plt.ylabel(r'$x_2$', fontsize=20, rotation='horizontal')\n",
    "    plt.title('ABCD'[k], fontsize=25)\n",
    "    plt.axhline(0, color='black')\n",
    "    plt.axvline(0, color='black')\n",
    "    plt.xlim([-max(np.abs(plt.axis())), max(np.abs(plt.axis()))])\n",
    "    plt.ylim([-max(np.abs(plt.axis())), max(np.abs(plt.axis()))])\n",
    "    plt.grid()\n",
    "    k+=1\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "fig.savefig('scatter.pdf')"
   ]
